  "closed_at": null,
  "body": "问题描述：\r\n给一个 `list` 组件通过 `flex` 属性设定宽度后，在 `list` 组件中的 `text` 组件设置 `lines` 属性无效。但在安卓中和网页中均能正常显示。但是若用 `width` 属性设定宽度，或者将 `list` 组件换成 `scroller` 组件均能正常显示。\r\n\r\nweex sdk 版本：0.9.4\r\n\r\n代码如下：\r\n```\r\n<template>\r\n  <div class=\"list-wrap\">\r\n    <div class=\"left\">\r\n      <list class=\"menu-left\">\r\n        <cell class=\"menu-item\" repeat=\"menu\">\r\n          <text class=\"menu-name\">{{ name }}</text>\r\n        </cell>\r\n      </list>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"right\">\r\n      <list class=\"menu-right\">\r\n        <cell class=\"menu-item\" repeat=\"menu\">\r\n          <text class=\"menu-name\">{{ name }}</text>\r\n        </cell>\r\n      </list>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n<script>\r\n  module.exports = {\r\n    data: {\r\n      menu: [\r\n        { name: 8.2, },\r\n        { name: 8.8, },\r\n        { name: 6.2, },\r\n        { name: 9.8, },\r\n        { name: 6.8, },\r\n        { name: '用了一段很长的文字描述测试文字换行的时候显示', },\r\n      ],\r\n    },\r\n  };\r\n</script>\r\n<style>\r\n  .list-wrap {\r\n    margin-top: 30px;\r\n    flex-direction: row;\r\n    flex: 1;\r\n    background-color: #fff;\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  .left {\r\n    flex: 3;\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  .right {\r\n    flex: 9;\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  .menu-left {\r\n    background-color: #f8f8f8;\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  .menu-right {\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  .menu-name {\r\n    padding-left: 20px;\r\n    padding-right: 20px;\r\n    padding-top: 36px;\r\n    padding-bottom: 36px;\r\n    lines: 3;\r\n    text-overflow: ellipsis;\r\n    color: #666;\r\n    font-size: 24px;\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  .menu-item {\r\n    border-top-width: 1px;\r\n    border-top-style: solid;\r\n    border-top-color: #ededed;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n```\r\n![qq20170111-0](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7367678/21839814/c4131ae8-d814-11e6-8091-bd5ea3445126.png)\r\n\r\n安卓中的效果如下：\r\n![wechatimg22](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7367678/21839933/7d360530-d815-11e6-9317-c402680461ee.jpeg)\r\n\r\n将左边的 `list` 改为 `scroller` 后的效果如下：\r\n![f2facc55-cd63-47dc-a73e-66fa6140a903](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7367678/21839922/70306d76-d815-11e6-9c39-2b2c94e89fd7.png)\r\n",
